Review:
First time trying The Wood Tavern's food, wanted a big juicy burger so I got The Wood Burger, well it wasn't juicy at all, very dense, skimpy on the lettuce, tiny tomato and I couldn't even taste the hickory bacon ranch at all and to me my burger patty was burnt, not worth 22$ that's all I tasted was burnt. Fries were crispy and the wings were alright, the sauces I got were good, honey dill and some honey mustard I think? The taste just fell flat and charred.

@TheWoodTavern, Thanks for the response, I did make an issue on Skip and it wasn't full filled. Thanks
@TheWoodTavern, thank you but you didn't have to do that, nothing yet. I appreciate the gesture.
